Mizuki: (Did Li'l Bro draw a really bad assignment or something?)
Mizuki: I hope I get something easy... Please!
Mizuki: Hey!
Mizuki: This one's in the bag...!
Mizuki: Someone! I need an accessory with a ribbon motif!
